---
title: Asian-Style Chicken & Ginger Slaw Bowl with Roasted Peanuts & Cashews
description: The great thing about a slaw bowl is how customisable it can be! Dress this one up with sweet and soy chicken
with a punch of ginger and a radish and corn slaw sprinkled with a nutty finish. The final flourish is a garlic aioli.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
